Chriſts holy paſſions and extaſies. Yea, we finde the Son of God our Saviour Jeſus Chriſt (who enjoyed the greateſt ſerenity, and exacteſt harmony of body and minde) did not carry on an Apathy, but anſwered in his temper the ſtroke and tune of the occaſion;

ſometimes he rejoyced in ſpirit; otherwhile he grieved, ſighed, weeped,
